Package: matchbook
Type: Package
Title: Wrapper for the Matchbook.com API
Version: 1.0.5
Date: 2017-08-16
Author: Niall Fitzgerald
Maintainer: Niall Fitzgerald <nfitzgerald@xanadu.ie>
Description: This provides a wrapper for the some basic functionality around
    the Matchbook.com REST API. It features calls to get events, markets and runners
    in data frame format. It features functions for bet placement and position
    managment and also allows reporting of settled bet transactions. Note: this
    library uses the back-lay format. The default for odds type, currency and
    language are set according to those of the registered user account.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0),
    httr,
    jsonlite
License: MIT
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
